b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":581,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"Astral Pieces Available from Quests in Preparation for Astral Raids!","message":"<div>As of <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1562824800\\"><\/span>, Astral Pieces, an item used to challenge Astral Raids, will now drop from main campaign quests and event quests!<\/div><div>\\u30fbAstral Raids will be available starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1563602400\\"><\/span>. Keep an eye out for a future notification with more information.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/011f0d1be28deb9ad8be621a29e7529a.png\\"><\/div><div>\\u25a0Astral Raids Overview<\/div><div>\\u30fbAstral Raids are event quests where you can fight against past raid bosses, but they are only available on the weekends.<\/div><div>\\u30fbTo challenge Astral Raids quests, you will need to use Astral Pieces.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Astral Pieces<\/div><div>\\u30fbAstral pieces can be obtained by clearing main campaign quests and event quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbYou will not receive Astral Pieces for clearing The Mercurial Gauntlet quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbYou will not receive Astral Pieces for clearing quests while astral raids are active.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe maximum number of Astral Pieces you can hold is 300.<\/div><div>\\u30fbIf you obtain Astral Pieces after reaching the limit, those Astral Pieces will be lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1562824800,"prev_article_id":"553","next_article_id":"573","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/011f0d1be28deb9ad8be621a29e7529a.png","update_time":1569488897}}}'